div.p:
What can you propound to your ſelves? if you are for good things, ſo are we; if for a Free State and Common-wealth, ſo are we;
if againſt a Single perſon ſo are we; if for Reformation, ſo are we; if for godlineſs and the Nations to be exalted in Righteouſneſs,
ſo are we; Why do we differ in the form and way to it?
